## Why This Is Asked
Assesses robust log parsing across mixed formats, errors within multi-line entries, and compressed archives; tests mastery of shell tooling and edge-case handling.

## Key Concepts
- UNIX pipelines, find, zcat, and awk state machines
- Handling mixed text/JSON formats
- Multi-line entries and per-entry counting
- Skipping unreadable files and efficient streaming

## Code Example
