- **Missing timestamps or time zones:** Use explicit timezone handling with TZ environment variable, implement default-fallback logic for lines missing timestamps, or enrich with file modification time as surrogate
- **Large log sets and memory usage:** Replace awk with streaming aggregation using associative arrays flushed periodically, implement parallel processing with xargs -P, or consider sampling strategies for extremely high-volume traces

